    "chemicalDescription": [
      "r-(sh-Polypeptide-47 sh-Polypeptide-146) is a single chain recombinant peptide, produced by fermentation in E. coli. The starting gene is synthesized by the fusion of the gene from sh-Polypeptide-47 and sh-Polypeptide-146. The fusion peptide contains 246 amino acids which may contain disulfide bonds and/or glycosylation, and consists of the proper sequence of the 20 standard amino acids."
